claim.claim-text:
35. An irrigation drip emitter comprising:
an emitter body for mounting to a drip line, the emitter body having an inlet portion, a pressure reducing portion, and an outlet portion, the inlet portion, the pressure reducing portion, and the outlet portion being in fluid communication,
the outlet portion having a bottom wall defining in part a bath where fluid passes before discharging from the drip line, the bottom wall having an inner surface in the bath and an opposite facing exterior surface;
a projection extending from the exterior surface;
the outlet portion having a first thickness at only the bottom wall and a second thickness at the bottom wall and the projection, the second thickness being greater than the first thickness.
